title: JooBra
author: JooBra
content: Since I'm a Formula 1 fan since when I was a kid and last couple of years I was playing Fantasy F1 I made a topic for Fantasy F1 league. The name of the league is “BitcoinTalk Fantasy F1” and the code for the league is C49WHE69M03. Everyone is free to join and along the season we can discuss here the progression of our teams and drivers. There are so many of ways where you can go with picking drivers.
